# PBF Cache Directory

This directory stores OSM PBF files downloaded from Geofabrik.

## Usage

Place your `.osm.pbf` files here:
- `zhejiang-latest.osm.pbf` - Zhejiang province
- `jiangsu-latest.osm.pbf` - Jiangsu province
- etc.

## Download

Download PBF files from: https://download.geofabrik.de/

Example:
```bash
wget https://download.geofabrik.de/asia/china/zhejiang-latest.osm.pbf \
  -O pbf_cache/zhejiang-latest.osm.pbf
```

## Note

PBF files are large and should NOT be committed to git.
